cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

The paper deals with deep neural networks for image classification, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of spiking neural networks for unsupervised learning also falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the resilience of the network to input perturbations, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the application of the network to autonomous vehicles and robotics suggests a potential connection to systems and control (cs.SY).
